Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,发旋攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
