Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他很快就会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在做梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
