Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.05,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.97,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}虽然害怕…但还是想！
